新加坡国立大学尤洋教授团队、韩国科学技术院 John Kim 教授团队、北京大学杨仝老师团队、中国科学院计算技术研究所王颖老师团队获得 2023 年奥林帕斯先锋奖。 全球求解难题，华为悬红 200 万"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-bc684a8f0ed2d0a643599e33755b33af_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "293 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/657216824"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIk+2ngNug8dwgEAMaCTEwODMyNjE2NSCS2cqyBjAAONABQANyCTY1NzIxNjgyNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1716791247.999739", "card_id": "Q_656735704", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《红楼梦》为什么要给丫鬟和下人发工资？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "贾府里有三等丫头，二等丫头，有的三百钱一个月，有的五百钱，像袭人这种大丫头更是一两银子一个月。可是，她们不是奴才吗？生死都操纵在主人手里，随手可以送人，甚至指配婚姻，那么，为什么还要给他们发工资呢？不发工资会怎么样？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "97 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656735704"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ik+2ngNug8dwgEAMaCTEwODIxOTM3OSDLr7KyBjAAOCpABHIJNjU2NzM1NzA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1716791248.1861", "card_id": "Q_657300970", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 89}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "巴林、埃及、突尼斯、阿联酋国家元首将访华，此行有哪些看点？释放出怎样的信号？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "外交部发言人华春莹宣布： 应国家主席习近平邀请，巴林国王哈马德、埃及总统塞西、突尼斯总统赛义德、阿联酋总统穆罕默德将于 5 月 28 日至 6 月 1 日对中国进行国事访问并出席中国—阿拉伯国家合作论坛第十届部长级会议开幕式。（央视新闻客户端）更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-ce17db93e6875078ce80e7d91a8bc023_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "95 